channel.description:
[center][b]Worldz of Gamerz[/b][/center]
Hey moparscape i am Mattredd9395. I am the founder of Worldz of Gamerz, I am looking for a team that is welling to be part of the Worldz of Gamerz! I am looking for (2) programmers, (1) web developer, (1) GFX Designer. WOG is currently new so i am also looking for forum moderators(4). If you are interested in working with the WOG Team or Staff fill out an application and post it on here. Thanks for your time Moparscape.
